high_descs: walk forwards to the kitchen counter at the end of the room
grab the butter knife off of the kitchen counter
turn right and walk over to the sink on the left
slice up the potato in the center of the sink there
place the knife down in the sink
grab a potato slice out of the sink
turn left and walk forwards to the microwave at the end of the room
place the potato slice in the microwave and cook it, then take it back out
turn left and walk to the garbage bin to your right just behind the fridge
place the cooked potato slice inside of the garbage bin
anns.task_desc: place a cooked potato slice inside of the garbage bin

high_descs: Walk across the room to where the toaster is on the counter.
Pick up the metal butter knife that is on the counter in front of the toaster.
Turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink
Slice up the potato that is in the sink basin.
Put the metal knife into the sink basin tip down.
Pick up a piece of sliced potato.
Turn left and walk over to the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave and place the piece of sliced potato inside, microwave the piece of sliced potato for a couple seconds, then open the microwave, remove it, and close the door.
Turn left and begin walking forward, then turn right and walk up to the fridge, turn left again and begin across the room, then turn right and walk up to the small blue bin to the left of the fridge.
Place the heated piece of sliced potato in the back left corner of the blue bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated piece of sliced potato in a blue bin.

high_descs: Walk to the toaster ahead of you.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Walk to the sink to the right of the coffee maker.
Cut up the potato in the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up a piece of the potato from the sink.
Turn to your left and walk to the red microwave.
Heat up the piece of potato in the microwave and then pick up the piece of potato.
Turn to your left and walk to the blue trash can to the left of the fridge.
Place the piece of potato into the blue trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a cut up piece of microwaved potato into the blue trash can.

high_descs: Walk to the counter with the toaster on it.
Pick up knife from counter.
Turn right, walk to sink, turn left to face sink.
Cut a slice from the potato in the sink.
Pick up the potato slice from the sink.
Turn left, walk to microwave.
Put potato slice in microwave and cook it.
Take potato slice from the microwave.
Take potato slice from the microwave, turn left, walk past refrigerator, turn right to face the garbage can.
Throw the potato slice in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a cooked potato slice.

high_descs: Walk to the counter then take a step to your left.
Pick up the knife that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the sink then turn left to face it.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Brown the slice of potato in the microwave and then get it back out and close the door.
Take two or three steps to your right so you are facing the blue garbage.
Put the slice of potato in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a browned slice of potato in the garbage.
